<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Redefinir senha</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="/imagem/favic.png" type="image/png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/auth.css">
  <style>
    body { min-height: 100vh; font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; display: grid; place-items: center; color: #103310; }
    .card { width: min(100%, 460px); background: #fff; border: 1px solid #d5dde6; border-radius: 10px; padding: 36px; box-shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(15, 35, 25, 0.14); }
    h1 { font-size: 1.55rem; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #0d311d; }
    p { color: #405347; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 22px; }
    form { display: grid; gap: 16px; }
    label { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    input { width: 100%; border: 1px solid #d5dde6; padding: 0 14px; }
    .error { padding: 12px 14px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.92rem; color: #8a1f1f; background: #fdecec; border: 1px solid #f5b8b8; }
    .actions { display: grid; gap: 12px; margin-top: 4px; }
    .submit, .help { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 48px; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="card">
    <h1>Redefinir senha</h1>
    <p>Digite sua nova senha para voltar a acessar o sistema.</p>

    <form action="/redefinir-senha/<%= token %>" method="POST">
      <% if (typeof erro !== 'undefined' && erro) { %>
        <div class="error"><%= erro %></div>
      <% } %>

      <div>
        <label for="senha">Nova senha</label>
        <input id="senha" name="senha" type="password" autocomplete="new-password" required>
      </div>

      <div>
        <label for="confirmarSenha">Confirmar nova senha</label>
        <input id="confirmarSenha" name="confirmarSenha" type="password" autocomplete="new-password" required>
      </div>

      <div class="actions">
        <button class="submit" type="submit">Salvar nova senha</button>
        <a class="help" href="/login">Voltar para o login</a>
      </div>
    </form>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
